text: Hossein Vafaei (; born 15 October 1994) is an Iranian snooker player. He was the first professional player from Iran. He won his first ranking title at the 2022 Snooker Shoot Out. He beat Mark Williams 1–0 (71–0) in the final. == References == Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Iranian snooker players
